1
00:00:00,083 --> 00:00:02,166
From the investigation room—it’s very close

2
00:00:02,166 --> 00:00:06,208
So those in the first group cell, the other cells, and the solitary cells, all heard the torture

3
00:00:06,791 --> 00:00:08,125
This is the investigation room

4
00:00:09,291 --> 00:00:11,291
They used this door to hang the tortured prisoners

5
00:00:12,291 --> 00:00:14,166
Like the other door, and this one too

6
00:00:14,208 --> 00:00:19,125
Sometimes they would hang three people at the same time

7
00:00:19,541 --> 00:00:21,708
You could only hear the groaning of those tortured

8
00:00:22,458 --> 00:00:24,125
Sometimes the beating happened here

9
00:00:24,166 --> 00:00:26,208
Then we’d hear that they were outside the investigation room

10
00:00:26,208 --> 00:00:28,291
They might drag someone out here and start beating him
